    "properties_description": "The main therapeutic properties of Vincetoxicum eurychiton are anti-inflammatory, which is attributed to the presence of flavonoids and saponins that reduce the production of pro-inflammatory cytokines and enzymes, as well as antioxidant, due to the scavenging activity of phenolic acids and ascorbic acid that neutralize free radicals and protect cells from oxidative damage, analgesic and antipyretic, resulting from the inhibition of the enzyme cyclooxygenase and the release of histamine, and hepatoprotective, characterized by the activation of antioxidant enzymes and the reduction of liver damage markers, all of which are mediated by the bioactive compounds present in the plant.",
